posts.post_content:
Just got around to making a trade list for some other trades going on, and decided I really like trading, so why not put the list out here on the board?

I primarily am looking for:

* Any complete sets, any grade (pre-1973)
* Partial sets (with stars and RCs, not just commons), any grade
* ANY HOFers in pre-war - usually collect low grade due to affordability
* Will also consider 1948-68 key RCs or stars like Mantle/Williams/Robinson
* T206 Ty Cobb (any), low grade or Authentic Only
* Unusual pre-1940 Lou Gehrig items


Here is what I have. If the list comes out all scrambled from Excel, please PM me with your email address and I can send the excel file as an attachment. Please ask for grades or pictures of anything ungraded on my list.

Thanks - now let's have some fun!
Mark
